quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  47,30,"Sinno Min kaajuno, Min kolleteno …ďe. Ganndiraa …ďe Ma'andeeji ma…ď…ďe …óiin; ko pellet, a nganndiratno …ďe ka konngol belngol. Allah non hino anndi golle mon …óeen."
  47,31,"Ma Min njarribo on, haa Min ngannda tii…ónii…ďe …ďen e mon, e mu√Ī√Īii…ďe …ďeen. Min njarriboo kadi kabaruuji mon."
  47,32,"Pellet, yeddu…ďe …ďeen …ďe paddi laawol Allah ngol, …ďe lunndii Nulaa…óo on …ďaawo nde peewal ngal …ďanngannde …ďe, …ďeen lorrataa Allah hay hu'unde. Ma O bonnu fii golle ma…ď…ďe …óeen."
  47,33,"Eey mon yo gooŇč…óin…ďe! …óoftee Allah, …óofto…óon Nulaa…óo on, wata on mbonnu golle mon …óeen."
  47,34,"Pellet, …ďeen yeddu…ďe …ďe sakkii e laawol Allah ngol, hooti …ďe maayi ko …ďe he'efer…ďe, Allah haforanoytaa …ďe."
  47,35,"Wota on lo'inkino, noddon e beldal, ko onon woni foolu…ďe …ďeen, Allah no wonndi e mon, O ustantaa on njo…ďdi golle mon …óeen."
  47,36,"Ganndee nguurndam aduna ko fijindaaru e mbelee…óe tan; hara le si on ngooŇč…óiii, on kulii [Allah], O ye…óay on njo…ďdi mon ndiin, o lamndotaako on jawle mon …óeen."
  47,37,"Si O aru la…ďndaade on fii majje, haa O du√Īii on (e mum), nguddon, O fe√Ī√Īina noon konnaagu mon ngun."
  47,38,"Hey mon onon …óoo, ho…óon noddee e nafqugol fii laawol Allah ngol. Hino e mo'on wuddat…ďe. Kala non guddu…óo, haray ko hoore-makko o wuddani. Ko Allah woni Galo On, onon ngoni wa'asu…ďe …ďeen. Si on nduŇčtii, O wa…ótitira on wo…ď…ďe goo, hara non …ďeen mba'ataa wano mon."